Waꞌanʉ Nindsʉnꞌa̱jtʉm Jesukristʉ mgunuꞌxʉdʉ es ja Dios mmoꞌoyʉdʉ tsyojkʉn esʉ Espíritʉ Santʉ mmʉtꞌítʉdʉ nidʉgekyʉ miidsʉty.
Kyajts xymyooydyʉ jembyʉ ka̱jxwíjʉn ja ja̱ꞌa̱y diꞌibʉty kʉxʉꞌktʉp ko ñigopkꞌa̱jttʉp ma̱ ja mʉbʉjkpʉtʉjkʉty. Kyajts ʉj nduñʉ kwentʉ pʉn pʉ́n yʉꞌʉjʉty, jaꞌa ko Dios kyaj tpayoꞌoy wingʉꞌʉy agʉꞌʉy éxtʉm ñayyajkʉxeꞌegyʉty.
Mʉguꞌugítʉty, min nꞌokꞌyajtuꞌunʉm éxtʉmʉ ijxpajtʉn diꞌibʉ ʉdsa̱jtʉm nidʉgekyʉ tʉ nꞌijxʉm oynʉꞌʉnʉn ma̱ njikyꞌa̱jtʉnꞌa̱jtʉm. Ko tuꞌugʉ ja̱ꞌa̱y dyajtiꞌigyʉdʉ ꞌyayuk o ttuñ ja kajxyꞌátypyʉ es tfirmaraty yajxón, ni pʉ́n mba̱a̱t tkapuwitsy es ni mba̱a̱t tkayajmʉ́jʉ.
